<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="tarmii.theme"
      lang="en">

<body>
    <metal:main fill-slot="content">
    <div id="content">

        <h1 class="documentFirstHeading" i18n:translate="heading_write_new_ question">Write a New Question</h1>

        <h4 i18n:translate="label_choose_question_type">Choose a question type from the options below</h4>

        <div id="choose-question-type"
            tal:define="plone_view context/@@plone_portal_state;
                        portal_url plone_view/portal_url">
            <div id="simple-question">
                <form method="post" action="++add++upfront.assessmentitem.content.assessmentitemcontainer">
                    <input name="questiontype" type="hidden" value="simple"/>
                    <input alt="Free-form or multiple-choice question" src="images/simplequestion.png" title="Free-form or multiple-choice question" border="1" type="image" i18n:attributes="alt title" tal:attributes="src string:${portal_url}/++resource++tarmii.theme/images/simplequestion.png">
                </form>

                <div class="heading" i18n:translate="heading_simple_question">Simple Question</div>

                <div class="explanation" i18n:translate="simple_question_explanation">
                    Use this type for simple free-form questions that may or may
                    not have a multiple-choice answer.
                </div>

            </div>
            <div id="multipart-question">
                <form method="post" action="++add++upfront.assessmentitem.content.assessmentitemcontainer">
                    <input name="questiontype" type="hidden" value="multipart"/>
                    <input type="image" border="1" title="Multipart question" src="/images/multipartquestion.png" alt="Multipart question" i18n:attributes="alt title" tal:attributes="src string:${portal_url}/++resource++tarmii.theme/images/multipartquestion.png">
                </form>

                <div class="heading" i18n:translate="heading_multipart_question">Multipart Question</div>

                <div class="explanation" i18n:translate="multipart_question_explanation">
                    These questions share a common introduction for which several questions are then asked. The questions can be independent or they can have some dependence.
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="visualClear"></div>

    </div>
    </metal:main>
</body>
</html>

